From f7091131bce9784e698e1047c3cc22a826e0225e Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Shayne Chen <shayne.chen@mediatek.com>
Date: Tue, 29 Apr 2025 15:17:14 +0800
Subject: [PATCH 4/4] mtk: hostapd: fix compile warning of hostapd

fix complie warnings for hostapd_cli cmd
The fourth parameter should be int.

Fix compile warning of const qualifier.

Fix compile warning of undeclared data structure.

Fix build warning log of emlsr
warnig: passing argument 2 of 'hostapd_drv_set_eml_omn' discards
'const' qualifier from pointer target type [-Wdiscarded-qualifiers]
struct mld_link_info is not visible in drv_ops layer, so pass
valid_links into it to prevent compile warnings.

fixup! mtk: hostapd: add support for EPCS
(1) Access to out-of-scope EPCS data structures
(2) Implicit type conversion

fixup! mtk: hostapd: Add support for TSF offset

fixup! mtk: hostapd: support MLD AP affiliated link removal

fixup! mtk: hostapd: add 802.1X support AP MLD
hostapd_is_mld_ap() is declared in ieee802_11.h, include it.

fix wbcs values when pp is enabled
Fix compile warning
../src/ap/ieee802_11.c: In function 'hostapd_eid_wb_channel_switch':
../src/ap/ieee802_11.c:7977:17: warning: implicit declaration of function 'punct_update_legacy_bw' [-Wimplicit-function-declaration]
7977 |                 punct_update_legacy_bw(punct_bitmap,
